<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@700&family=Quicksand:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/bootstrap_customize.css"/>
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/common.css"/>
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/home.css"/>
    <title>Home</title>
</head>
<body>
{{>part/nav}}
<div id="main-container" class="d-flex justify-content-center quicksand nskr">
    <div id="carousel-container" class="m-4">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mb-4">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="35" height="35" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-emoji-smile" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                    <path d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 1 8 1a7 7 0 0 1 0 14zm0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16z"/>
                    <path d="M4.285 9.567a.5.5 0 0 1 .683.183A3.498 3.498 0 0 0 8 11.5a3.498 3.498 0 0 0 3.032-1.75.5.5 0 1 1 .866.5A4.498 4.498 0 0 1 8 12.5a4.498 4.498 0 0 1-3.898-2.25.5.5 0 0 1 .183-.683zM7 6.5C7 7.328 6.552 8 6 8s-1-.672-1-1.5S5.448 5 6 5s1 .672 1 1.5zm4 0c0 .828-.448 1.5-1 1.5s-1-.672-1-1.5S9.448 5 10 5s1 .672 1 1.5z"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center fs-1 ms-3">Welcome to SQL Practice!</div>
        </div>
        <div id="carousel-with-captions" class="carousel carousel-dark slide border border-2" data-bs-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="/static/img/carousel/carousel1.png" class="d-block w80">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-light text-dark p-2 border border-dark">
                        <b>기본 문법부터 다중 테이블 연산까지! 알아두면 유익한 SQL 문법들을 학습해보세요!</b>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/static/img/carousel/carousel4.png" class="d-block w80">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-light text-dark p-2 border border-dark">
                        <b>배운 내용을 잘 이해했는지 확인할 수 있는 테스트 기능을 제공합니다.</b>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/static/img/carousel/carousel5.png" class="d-block w90">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-light text-dark p-2 border border-dark">
                        <b>테스트 후 결과를 바로 확인할 수 있습니다.</b>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/static/img/carousel/carousel6.png" class="d-block w80">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-light text-dark p-2 border border-dark">
                        <b>Q/A 게시판을 활용하여 질문을 남겨주세요. 버그 제보 게시판도 마련되어 있으니 여러분들의 피드백을 환영합니다.</b>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/static/img/carousel/carousel7.png" class="d-block w80">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-light text-dark p-2 border border-dark">
                        <b>알아두면 유익한 외부 참고 자료들도 같이 알려드립니다!</b>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel-with-captions" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel-with-captions" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
    {{>part/accountinfo}}
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
